    <item>
      <title>英国经济：薪资数据火热，英国央行加重利率谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/uk-economy-hot-wage-data-adds-to-boe-caution-on-rates-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受私营部门薪资大幅上涨的推动，截至 10 月的三个月内，英国常规工资增长速度超过预期，凸显出英国央行对降息的谨慎态度。彭博经济的 Dan Hanson 对数据进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/uk-economy-hot-wage-data-adds-to-boe-caution-on-rates-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:01:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工资上涨后交易员预计英国央行降息幅度将减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在截至十月的三个月内，英国工资增长速度超过预期，货币市场大幅解除了对英国降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦未能向被征用土地的白人农民支付赔偿金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/zimbabwe-fails-to-pay-white-farmers-who-had-land-expropriated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的白人商业种植者表示，政府未能向征用土地的农民支付 3.31 亿美元的部分赔偿金，但向未参与协议的其他农民进行了补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/zimbabwe-fails-to-pay-white-farmers-who-had-land-expropriated</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:25:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在议会提出“一国一选举”法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-introduces-one-nation-one-election-bill-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政府已向议会提交了一项法案草案，提议在全国范围内同时举行选举，这是印度试图改变世界最大民主国家的选举格局的又一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-introduces-one-nation-one-election-bill-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:23:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
