    <item>
      <title>英国工资增长势将巩固英国央行的谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-wage-growth-accelerates-more-than-forecast-to-5-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在私营部门薪资大幅上涨的推动下，英国十月季度常规工资增长速度超过预期，凸显出英国央行对降息的谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-wage-growth-accelerates-more-than-forecast-to-5-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:08:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中国和特朗普影响，亚洲货币指数跌至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/asian-currency-index-drops-to-two-year-low-as-china-trump-weigh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国经济前景的悲观情绪以及对特朗普政府将推动美元上涨的猜测，亚洲货币指数跌至两年多以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/asian-currency-index-drops-to-two-year-low-as-china-trump-weigh</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透社称中国计划实现 5% 左右的增长目标，增加赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/china-plans-about-5-gdp-target-in-2025-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引两位未透露姓名的消息人士的话称，中国领导人计划将明年的经济增速目标设定在 5% 左右，并将预算赤字提高到国内生产总值 (GDP) 的 4%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/china-plans-about-5-gdp-target-in-2025-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元下跌至接近日本央行密切关注的 155 水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/yen-s-slide-brings-it-near-closely-watched-155-level-before-boj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元在过去一周内迅速下跌至 155 关口，策略师们警告称，日元进一步走软可能引发当局的口头干预，并给日本央行增加加息压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/yen-s-slide-brings-it-near-closely-watched-155-level-before-boj</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 02:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治不确定性拖累法国经济增长前景放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命法国一年内第四位总理几天后，法国央行下调了国内增长预期，央行称政治动荡拖累了家庭和企业信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
